{"tid":220881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北大法學教授：外國籍無資格佔中倡港獨 應被逐出境】","createTime":"2017-04-28T09:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T16:11:58.000Z","uid":28366,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fee41f298ba57e986d876a8ec4918fbedc21be4","tid":220881,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170428/large/1493355602_2825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170428%2Flarge%2F1493355602_2825.jpg&h=cfd4b546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北大法學院教授陳端洪出席《紫荊》一國兩制論壇時，質疑那些活躍於佔中、主張港獨的人，是否有外國戶籍，反問這此人憑甚麼對國家提出政治主張，直言若他們不是中國籍，就沒有資格提出有關主張，並應被驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n前港澳辦副主任、全國港澳研究會會長徐澤致辭時稱，未來要加強研究一國兩制和《基本法》基礎言論，以全面準確理解一國兩制和《基本法》，明白一國兩制「為何而生、往哪裡去」，當中要加強《基本法》的宣傳教育推廣，提高行政、立法、司法人員遵守、維護《基本法》的能力。<br />\n<br />\n徐亦表示，中央落實一國兩制和《基本法》的決心堅定不移，即使近年一國兩制的落實出現新情況和新問題，都沒有甚麼可怕，問題是怎樣面對，強調只要堅定不移，沿正確方向前進就可。  <br />\n<br />\n[url][/<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170428/56625088url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170428%2F56625088url%5D&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=0bd76701\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170428%2F56625088url%5D&h=780837eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170428/56625088url]</a>"},{"pid":"19b16a61f993a09263f8bfa582eea0cdae751ff5","tid":220881,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"遂左 你地阿head先啦<br />\n<br />\n家人係外國 有咩資格對我地中國指手畫腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d6c12e4f13f6b53fb69edd1dec2499a64738f2","tid":220881,"uid":35236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"我有bno 可唔可以逐我<img src=\"/a